title: 圈地插件不行An internal error occurred while attempting to perform this command
author: 包子戴
txt_content:
An internal error occurred while attempting to perform this command
怎么回事

replies.author: woshiquanlai
replies.txt_content: 领地插件……有错误，具体错误不明，因为lz没有说明具体情况。建议lz换一个领地插件，然后确定服务端没显示【warning】之类的，再看清楚圈画工具之后，用圈画工具圈点，输入/res create 领地名  如果还是有错………………………………………………无能为力。

replies.author: wolski
replies.txt_content: 使用对应版本插件即可
